title: The Wailing Perversion
summary: The Wailing Perversion Manhwa Ananta, a barbaric warrior cursed by a demon god. In order to punish the incarnation of the wings, who turned his fate into a tragedy, he endlessly feasts on demon gods in a story of blood, sweat, flesh, and bones that yearns for revenge.
